  "common_pattern": "All integrations: (1) check extension_loaded(), return NOT_AVAILABLE if missing; (2) hook native class methods with \\DDTrace\\trace_method / install_hook; (3) populate SpanData with name/resource/type/meta/metrics; (4) return Integration::LOADED",

